cast.overview: Joe Gideon is at the top of the heap, one of the most successful directors and choreographers in musical theater. But he can feel his world slowly collapsing around him - his obsession with work has almost destroyed his personal life, and only his bottles of pills keep him going.
cast.title: All That Jazz

details.biography: K.C. Townsend (July 10, 1949 - April 6, 1989; born "Kathleen Fay Sullivan") was an American actress who had played bit parts in several movies and television programs. She graduated from Waseca High School in 1959 and attended the University of Minnesota from 1959 to 1960. Kathi went to New York to pursue her acting career in the spring of 1960 and lived for many years at 200 W 58th St. - Apt. 5C.  She died on 6 April 1989 in New York, New York, USA.
details.name: K.C. Townsend
